---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro'
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro'
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro'
import AboutSection from '../components/AboutSection.astro'
---
<MainLayout title="About — Dsin Manufacturing">
  <Navbar />
  <main class="py-12">
    <AboutSection />
    <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-8">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Company Profile</h3>

      <div class="mt-4 text-slate-700 space-y-4">
        <p>
          Dsin Manufacturing is a precision engineering company focused on developing, producing, 
          and supplying a wide range of equipment for the agriculture, plantation, fabrication, industrial, 
          and automotive sectors. With extensive experience and expertise in modern manufacturing technology, 
          the company is committed to delivering accurate, efficient, and high-quality engineering solutions.
          Supported by skilled professionals and industry-standard production facilities, Dsin Manufacturing is 
          dedicated to becoming a strategic partner for clients, helping enhance productivity, operational reliability, 
          and competitiveness through innovative engineering solutions.
        </p>

        <h4 class="font-semibold">Brief History</h4>
        <p>
          Founded as a small precision machining workshop, Dsin Manufacturing has grown into an industrial-scale 
          facility serving both local and international customers. Our growth has been driven by continuous 
          investment in 5-axis CNC machinery, automated inspection systems, and documented manufacturing practices 
          that ensure consistency and high standards.
        </p>

        <h4 class="font-semibold">Leadership & Organizational Structure</h4>
        <p>
          The company is led by an experienced management team with strong backgrounds in engineering 
          and mass production. Our organizational structure consists of dedicated divisions including Engineering, 
          Production, Quality Assurance, Logistics, and Customer Support. Each division works in an integrated 
          manner to meet clients’ technical and commercial needs with transparency and accountability.
        </p>

        <h4 class="font-semibold">Facilities & Capabilities</h4>
        <p>
          Our facility is equipped with multi-axis CNC machines, turning centers, automated assembly 
          lines. We also provide comprehensive engineering services such as CAD/CAM design, basic simulation, 
          rapid prototyping, and process optimization for both small-scale and high-volume production.
        </p>

        <h4 class="font-semibold">Quality & Certification</h4>
        <p>
          Dsin Manufacturing operates under strict quality procedures with full traceability 
          documentation for every production batch and implement both in-line and final inspections to ensure each 
          component meets the required specifications.
        </p>

        <h4 class="font-semibold">Industries Served</h4>
        <p>
          We serve a diverse range of sectors including Agriculture, Plantation, Fabrication, Industrial Equipment, 
          and Automotive. Our broad industry experience enables us to meet specialized requirements such as 
          precise tolerances, durable material specifications, and reliable quality-tracking processes essential 
          for high-performance operations.
        </p>

        <h4 class="font-semibold">Research & Innovation</h4>
        <p>
          Our R&D team collaborates closely with clients to develop practical and efficient engineering 
          solutions tailored to real operational needs. We focus on improving manufacturability, reducing 
          production costs, and enhancing equipment performance for agriculture, plantation, fabrication, industrial, 
          and automotive applications. We also explore the use of automation, digital monitoring, and process 
          optimization technologies to increase production efficiency and machine uptime.
        </p>

        <h4 class="font-semibold">Social & Environmental Responsibility</h4>
        <p>
          We are committed to responsible manufacturing practices that support sustainability in agriculture and industry. 
          Our initiatives include energy-efficient operations, proper waste management, and adherence to environmental 
          regulations. Dsin Manufacturing also prioritizes workplace safety and continuous human resource development 
          through structured training, ensuring a safe, ethical, and growth-oriented working environment.
        </p>

        <h4 class="font-semibold">Location & Contact</h4>
        <p>
          Our headquarters and production facility are located within an industrial zone. 
          For project inquiries or quotation requests, please visit our <a href="/contact" class="text-primary underline"> Contact</a> Or send email to <a href="mailto:support@dsinmanufacturing.com" class="text-primary">support@dsinmanufacturing.com</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</MainLayout>
